description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Upper Body Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency. The The Foundation Builder vibe means Strengthen weak points, rebuild, perfect the basics. This is especially good for Those coming back from injury or refining fundamentals..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Build upper body strength with Peter during all beginner friendly bodyweight exercises. ...
